text: @FedExHelp I have a package from the UK that was due to arrive in CA this morning, but it seems like due to a customs issue it's stuck in TN. I've been on hold +20 mins to try to reach the rep (Taylor) who left a message about it. How long should I anticipate being on hold? ðŸ˜¢
are you shitting me???? I spent over an hour on hold and then the @FedEx @FedExHelp phone line told me the number I'm trying to reach is unavailable??? oh that's nice. https://t.co/ZROxs2Tbht
@TheOneCalledEli @TheOneCalledEli: I'll be delighted to check on your shipment! Would you send the tracking # and delivery address? Sonia
@FedExHelp Thank you Sonia, just sent you a  Direct Message!
waiting on a DM reply from @FedExHelp. you're breaking my heart, Sonia. you made it sound like you genuinely wanted to help.

@TheOneCalledEli @TheOneCalledEli: Your shipment is currently in Memphis at our Hub, was due to arrive today, Friday and appears to have an operational delay. Please continue to track this shipment, will update to deliver on next business day Monday. Am sorry for delays.

@FedExHelp Can I please ask what an "operational delay" means? My concern is that there may be issues with customs preventing the package from traveling further into the states. Do you know who I could contact to ascertain if this is an issue, please?
